   <narrative xml:lang="EN">New toilets at a primary school in rural Kenya.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">It is estimated that over 620 million children worldwide, many of them in sub-Saharan Africa, do not have access to basic sanitation services in school. We are investing in brand new sanitation facilities at Kisimenyi Primary School which will include VIP latrines and urinals, a girls&apos; washroom and, for the first time at the school, proper hand-washing facilities.</narrative>
  </description>
